Yesterday was the worst day of my life 💔

I sent my sweet girl to heaven yesterday.

This is my love letter to you nibs:

Nibblet, I love you so much. You were there for me through it all. You helped me get through college, you helped me through relationships, you helped me with my alcoholism. 

I hope you felt like I was there for you this past year with your diabetes when you needed me. I hope you felt like I was there for you when you went through surgery for your bladder stones. I hope you know how loved you were and still are. 

You were my soul nibblet. A part of me died with you yesterday.

I don’t know how to do life without you. My life will never be the same. 

I woke up today and went to let you outside to feed you and to give you your shot 
When I walk downstairs, you should be there. 
When I sit on the couch or in my bed, you should be there. 
When I walk around the neighborhood, you should be there. 
When I look in the backseat of my car, you should be there. 

It happened so quick. The vet was wrong about the cancer. I thought you were okay. I’m so sorry I couldn’t fix it all for you. I thought l had more time with you. 

#doglossgrief

Happy Valentine’s Day to my favorite person 💗 //

Bruce, I don’t know how I would do this life without you. Thank you for always loving me and being there for me. Love you so much.

#valentinesday

I will miss you forever my sweet girl 🤍
